title: Drag Race Underdog Aiden Zhane Felt Ganged Up On ‘From Day One’
description: Aiden Zhane always stood out from the other queens on 'RuPaul's Drag Race' Season 12 but still held her own against performers like Gigi Goode and Brita Filter.
